<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">«إِذا بُعْثِرَ ما فِي الْقُبُورِ»</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> أثير فأخرج..<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">«حُصِّلَ ما فِي الصُّدُورِ»</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ميّز <span class="c2">«٢»</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
